{"tid":1282508,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史是勝利者寫的， 自殺是將話語權交到對方手上","createTime":"2019-07-03T15:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T17:21:56.000Z","uid":228701,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5206356f76f3d09eb17b830c7d67842f423bdba7","tid":1282508,"uid":228701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mO35duo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmO35duo.png&h=d8809407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你苦無出路，<br />\n你孤立無援，<br />\n你寢食不安，<br />\n然後你以為死諫是你唯一可以做的事。<br />\n<br />\n但是，<br />\n跳樓自殺並不會令你黯淡無光的人生變得有意義。<br />\n歷史是勝利者寫的，<br />\n自殺是將話語權交到對方手上。<br />\n你以為自己是烈士，<br />\n其實你只是數字。<br />\n<br />\n累了就抽離一下，<br />\n出門戴耳機聽音樂，<br />\n不要去多老人家的餐廳。<br />\n多閱讀文史哲書，<br />\n擴闊思路，方可找尋出路，<br />\n<br />\n你還有很多事可以做。"},{"pid":"226e06466454a20e7c10f8c549fb91b39a98826f","tid":1282508,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"Sugarfree巴打出圖救港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e04ae52fb4f6c67def57bd23a671777488a5850","tid":1282508,"uid":240869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15c4862fdcd71db44e0aeca9b4d5eb4e8d0543eb","tid":1282508,"uid":80107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:03:56.000Z","msg":"建議著校服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話哂都唔少中學生"},{"pid":"d87ae2f5c740ee3cf05e714c5bcd5813722c19c1","tid":1282508,"uid":228701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"226e06466454a20e7c10f8c549fb91b39a98826f","tid":1282508,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"Sugarfree巴打出圖救港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />